  <brief_title>Verification of the Efficacy/Safety of the Dual Drug Delivery for Hearing Loss</brief_title>
  <official_title>Verification of the Efficacy / Safety of the Dual Drug Injectable Delivery Vehicle for Treating Intractable Hearing Loss (Pilot Study)</official_title>
