  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is a prospective, randomized pilot study. To verify an efficacy and safety of the&#xD;
      dual drug injectable delivery vehicle, patients who have not responded to the existing&#xD;
      standard treatment will be enrolled. Hearing test and endoscopy of tympanic membrane will be&#xD;
      conducted after intratympanic treatment for evaluation.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
